# Salesforce Workflow Automation Project

## 📌 Problem Statement
Business wants to track high-value sales under an Opportunity and get notified when multiple high-value sales are created.

## 💡 Solution
A custom object "Sales" is created with a Master-Detail relationship to Opportunity. Automation is implemented using Workflow Rules.

## ⚙️ Features
- Custom Object (Sales)
- Master-Detail Relationship (Opportunity → Sales)
- Roll-Up Summary Fields
- Workflow Rule Automation
- Email Alerts
- Task Creation

## 🔁 Working
When 2 or more Sales records with Amount ≥ 100,000 are created under an Opportunity:
- Email notification is triggered
- Task is created for Opportunity Owner

## 📊 Result
The system successfully sends email alerts and creates tasks automatically.

## 🧪 Testing
- Created Opportunity
- Added 2 Sales records ≥ 100,000
- Email received successfully

## 🚀 Conclusion
Automation reduces manual effort and ensures timely notification of high-value opportunities.
